Technology speeds things up.

00:09:51.290 --> 00:09:52.664 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: It is
very interesting.

00:09:52.664 --> 00:09:55.120 align:middle line:84%
And every person comes
with a different set

00:09:55.120 --> 00:09:56.700 align:middle line:90%
