00:09:56.700 --> 00:09:59.400 align:middle line:84%
So the effects for each
individual at the end of it

00:09:59.400 --> 00:10:00.610 align:middle line:90%
are really quite different.

00:10:00.610 --> 00:10:03.080 align:middle line:84%
But you just mentioned
something a moment ago.

00:10:03.080 --> 00:10:05.820 align:middle line:84%
So you allowed the beta
function of your brain,

00:10:05.820 --> 00:10:08.960 align:middle line:84%
