of your brain, to interfere,

00:10:08.960 --> 00:10:10.210 align:middle line:90%
which it's doing with us all--

00:10:10.210 --> 00:10:11.330 align:middle line:90%
>>HARDT: Well, it's hard not to.

00:10:11.330 --> 00:10:12.420 align:middle line:90%
Because it's so automatic.

00:10:12.420 --> 00:10:13.180 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: It's so automatic.

00:10:13.180 --> 00:10:14.680 align:middle line:84%
And that's what I
want to get into.

00:10:14.680 --> 00:10:17.870 align:middle line:84%
