the Western culture.

00:10:20.770 --> 00:10:22.430 align:middle line:90%
>>HARDT: Reactive modes.

00:10:22.430 --> 00:10:23.609 align:middle line:90%
They react.

00:10:23.609 --> 00:10:24.900 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: And it's mostly beta?

00:10:24.900 --> 00:10:28.100 align:middle line:84%
I mean, it's being
charged by beta?

00:10:28.100 --> 00:10:30.720 align:middle line:84%
>>HARDT: Well, there's
tremendous stress and anxiety

00:10:30.720 --> 00:10:33.450 align:middle line:84%
in modern culture, whether
it's financial stress,

00:10:33.450 --> 00:10:37.180 align:middle line:84%
or relationship stress, or
related to the children,

00:10:37.180 --> 00:10:40.130 align:middle line:84%
