alpha and promotes

00:10:42.410 --> 00:10:45.390 align:middle line:84%
beta mind, busy mind,
the inner dialogues.

00:10:45.390 --> 00:10:49.110 align:middle line:84%
Especially the negative
dialogues sabotage your alpha.

00:10:49.110 --> 00:10:52.940 align:middle line:84%
And so you have a natural
predisposition to making alpha

00:10:52.940 --> 00:10:56.320 align:middle line:84%
because the generator
of alpha is a pacemaker

00:10:56.320 --> 00:10:59.816 align:middle line:84%
cells in the thalamus,
which is located about here,

00:10:59.816 --> 00:11:01.190 align:middle line:84%
middle of the
brain-- some people

00:11:01.190 --> 00:11:02.650 align:middle line:84%
call it a brain
within the brain.

00:11:02.650 --> 00:11:06.330 align:middle line:84%
And the pacemaker cells run
24 hours a day, 7 days a week,

00:11:06.330 --> 00:11:09.970 align:middle line:84%
always urging your brain,
be in alpha, be in alpha.

00:11:09.970 --> 00:11:12.440 align:middle line:84%
But what Shakespeare might
call the slings and arrows

00:11:12.440 --> 00:11:15.220 align:middle line:84%
of outrageous fortune,
or just daily stress,

00:11:15.220 --> 00:11:17.990 align:middle line:84%
sabotage the communication
of the thalamus

00:11:17.990 --> 00:11:19.670 align:middle line:90%
with the surface of your brain.

00:11:19.670 --> 00:11:24.860 align:middle line:84%
And so people have way less
alpha than is their endowment.

00:11:24.860 --> 00:11:25.800 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: I know.

00:11:25.800 --> 00:11:26.570 align:middle line:90%
It's so sad.

00:11:26.570 --> 00:11:29.710 align:middle line:84%
But that's the hallmark
of modern times.

00:11:29.710 --> 00:11:31.460 align:middle line:84%
And when I say modern
times, I mean really

00:11:31.460 --> 00:11:34.320 align:middle line:84%
since the industrialization
of the world that's

00:11:34.320 --> 00:11:35.990 align:middle line:90%
what became modern times.

00:11:35.990 --> 00:11:38.710 align:middle line:84%
>>HARDT: Well Thoreau
