and everything is provided for.

00:11:45.900 --> 00:11:48.943 align:middle line:84%
This is a state which
will promote higher alpha.

00:11:48.943 --> 00:11:52.920 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: But oddly,
because of the fear

00:11:52.920 --> 00:11:55.870 align:middle line:84%
and, as you say, this
reactive state of mind

00:11:55.870 --> 00:12:00.460 align:middle line:84%
you're in that is forcing
us into an overuse of beta,

00:12:00.460 --> 00:12:04.500 align:middle line:84%
it's even damaging the
way our beta functions.

00:12:04.500 --> 00:12:06.420 align:middle line:84%
Our beta's not even
functioning clearly.

00:12:06.420 --> 00:12:08.600 align:middle line:84%
And explain-- let's talk
about the brain states,

00:12:08.600 --> 00:12:10.450 align:middle line:90%
the aspects of brain function.

00:12:10.450 --> 00:12:13.340 align:middle line:84%
Let's talk about beta, and
what it's charged with doing,

00:12:13.340 --> 00:12:18.522 align:middle line:84%
and then go to alpha theta, and
then down into awake, delta.

00:12:18.522 --> 00:12:20.230 align:middle line:84%
Let's explain that a
little bit so people

00:12:20.230 --> 00:12:21.760 align:middle line:90%
know what the context is.

00:12:21.760 --> 00:12:24.430 align:middle line:84%
>>HARDT: Well, in
my research I've

00:12:24.430 --> 00:12:26.990 align:middle line:84%
developed a thing called
brain energy maps.

00:12:26.990 --> 00:12:28.780 align:middle line:84%
They're like
topological surfaces.

00:12:28.780 --> 00:12:31.620 align:middle line:84%
I call it the cartography
of consciousness.

00:12:31.620 --> 00:12:34.990 align:middle line:84%
And in this, I can see--
we've got 21 different moods

00:12:34.990 --> 00:12:37.960 align:middle line:84%
in the mood scales: anxiety,
depression, hostility,

00:12:37.960 --> 00:12:40.270 align:middle line:84%
friendly, clear thinking,
sleepy, unhappy, vigor,

00:12:40.270 --> 00:12:45.460 align:middle line:84%
things like that-- and I've
made four dimensional maps which

00:12:45.460 --> 00:12:48.345 align:middle line:84%
show literally the
landscape of the mind

00:12:48.345 --> 00:12:50.470 align:middle line:84%
and the brain in different
states of consciousness.

00:12:50.470 --> 00:12:54.220 align:middle line:84%
All the negative brain wave
states have elevated beta,

00:12:54.220 --> 00:12:58.020 align:middle line:84%
whether it's anxiety,
unhappiness, depression,

00:12:58.020 --> 00:13:01.900 align:middle line:84%
hostility, anger-- they
all have elevated beta

00:13:01.900 --> 00:13:06.084 align:middle line:84%
and reduced or profoundly
suppressed alpha.

00:13:06.084 --> 00:13:08.000 align:middle line:84%
So this is how most
people are walking around.

00:13:08.000 --> 00:13:10.620 align:middle line:84%
They don't have the
endowment of alpha,

00:13:10.620 --> 00:13:13.330 align:middle line:84%
and they have way more
beta than is healthy.

00:13:13.330 --> 00:13:14.870 align:middle line:84%
Beta's associated
with a whole range

00:13:14.870 --> 00:13:16.365 align:middle line:90%
of stress-related diseases.

00:13:16.365 --> 00:13:17.990 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: Well, let's
talk about those.

00:13:17.990 --> 00:13:21.470 align:middle line:84%
But also the point
I was getting to is,

00:13:21.470 --> 00:13:25.770 align:middle line:84%
because of the driving
forces for the boosted beta,

00:13:25.770 --> 00:13:27.980 align:middle line:84%
beta is also tasked
with that really

00:13:27.980 --> 00:13:29.240 align:middle line:90%
clear mental functioning.

00:13:29.240 --> 00:13:31.640 align:middle line:84%
Say, if you're an attorney
presenting a case in court,

00:13:31.640 --> 00:13:35.250 align:middle line:84%
you have to have really
clearly functioning beta.

00:13:35.250 --> 00:13:36.890 align:middle line:90%
Most of us aren't that clear.

00:13:36.890 --> 00:13:38.600 align:middle line:90%
Our memories are kind of off.

00:13:38.600 --> 00:13:40.959 align:middle line:90%
We're reactive.

00:13:40.959 --> 00:13:42.250 align:middle line:90%
You understand what I'm saying?

00:13:42.250 --> 00:13:43.960 align:middle line:84%
We're in high beta but
it's not functional beta.

00:13:43.960 --> 00:13:44.980 align:middle line:84%
>>HARDT: The reason
I'm pausing is

00:13:44.980 --> 00:13:46.970 align:middle line:84%
because there's two
very different ways

00:13:46.970 --> 00:13:48.179 align:middle line:90%
to have that clarity of mind.

00:13:48.179 --> 00:13:49.803 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: Good, so
let's talk about it.

00:13:49.803 --> 00:13:52.500 align:middle line:84%
>>HARDT: One is beta, stress,
anxiety, hostility, and so on.

00:13:52.500 --> 00:13:57.430 align:middle line:84%
Or if you let go of that and
you go into a high alpha state,

00:13:57.430 --> 00:14:00.260 align:middle line:84%
then you have a clarity of mind
