00:14:00.260 --> 00:14:04.010 align:middle line:84%
And it allows you access to your
creativity in ways that beta

00:14:04.010 --> 00:14:04.580 align:middle line:90%
doesn't.

00:14:04.580 --> 00:14:05.455 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Absolutely.

00:14:05.455 --> 00:14:07.180 align:middle line:84%
And the frequency
rise, you're looking

00:14:07.180 --> 00:14:08.180 align:middle line:90%
at a range of frequency.

00:14:08.180 --> 00:14:09.520 align:middle line:90%
And high alpha is right here.

00:14:09.520 --> 00:14:11.710 align:middle line:84%
Beta's here, high
