00:14:24.780 --> 00:14:26.720 align:middle line:84%
And so what we want
to do is we want

00:14:26.720 --> 00:14:28.580 align:middle line:84%
to help people slow
down their brains.

00:14:28.580 --> 00:14:30.590 align:middle line:84%
And in the course of
