00:14:30.590 --> 00:14:35.270 align:middle line:84%
how to stop the mind chatter,
especially the negative voices.

00:14:35.270 --> 00:14:38.740 align:middle line:84%
And one of the results
of the seven day

00:14:38.740 --> 00:14:43.780 align:middle line:84%
alpha one training are a 50%
percent increase in creativity.

00:14:43.780 --> 00:14:46.300 align:middle line:84%
That was a study we did with
Stanford Research Institute

00:14:46.300 --> 00:14:47.260 align:middle line:90%
scientists.

00:14:47.260 --> 00:14:51.590 align:middle line:84%
There's also an IQ boost
