00:14:51.590 --> 00:14:55.010 align:middle line:84%
And statistically, the
strongest effect of all

00:14:55.010 --> 00:14:57.230 align:middle line:90%
is improvement in relationships.

00:14:57.230 --> 00:14:59.380 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Yes, yes absolutely.

00:14:59.380 --> 00:15:00.440 align:middle line:90%
I can attest to that.

00:15:00.440 --> 00:15:02.950 align:middle line:84%
But it doesn't mean the ride
