00:15:02.950 --> 00:15:03.624 align:middle line:90%
>>HARDT: No.

00:15:03.624 --> 00:15:05.540 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: But there's
an improvement over all.

00:15:05.540 --> 00:15:06.220 align:middle line:84%
>>HARDT: But you
