Now, these are mainstays
in most people's diets.

00:15:37.460 --> 00:15:39.640 align:middle line:84%
Tell us what those
things do to the brain,

00:15:39.640 --> 00:15:42.370 align:middle line:84%
and then also why you
won't allow anybody

00:15:42.370 --> 00:15:45.130 align:middle line:84%
to eat that before coming
into brain training.

00:15:45.130 --> 00:15:47.180 align:middle line:84%
>>HARDT: Well, people
can eat what they want.

00:15:47.180 --> 00:15:49.006 align:middle line:90%
We recommend.

00:15:49.006 --> 00:15:50.505 align:middle line:84%
We don't have
policemen at the door.

00:15:50.505 --> 00:15:51.590 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: That is true.

00:15:51.590 --> 00:15:57.750 align:middle line:84%
>>HARDT: But the
