people even accidentally get

00:18:36.110 --> 00:18:38.194 align:middle line:84%
some garlic, they're going
to come in the next day

00:18:38.194 --> 00:18:39.776 align:middle line:84%
and they're going
to be more agitated,

00:18:39.776 --> 00:18:41.700 align:middle line:84%
and their alpha levels
are going to be lower.

00:18:41.700 --> 00:18:43.380 align:middle line:84%
There's even an Arab
proverb that said,

00:18:43.380 --> 00:18:45.230 align:middle line:84%
after the devil had
done his dirty work

00:18:45.230 --> 00:18:47.150 align:middle line:84%
in the Garden of Eden,
when he walked out,

00:18:47.150 --> 00:18:50.570 align:middle line:84%
where his first foot went,
that was where garlic grew.

00:18:50.570 --> 00:18:53.540 align:middle line:84%
And where his second foot fell,
that was where onions grew.

00:18:53.540 --> 00:18:57.000 align:middle line:84%
So it's known in many cultures
that onions and garlic are

00:18:57.000 --> 00:19:00.650 align:middle line:84%
inimical to, shall we
say, spiritual growth.

00:19:00.650 --> 00:19:02.450 align:middle line:90%
Even calmness of mind.

00:19:02.450 --> 00:19:06.350 align:middle line:84%
I've had many people who eat
cloves of garlic a day say,

00:19:06.350 --> 00:19:10.360 align:middle line:84%
