Now, we could be a
little less sexist

00:19:59.120 --> 00:20:01.036 align:middle line:84%
and say, breakfast like
a king or queen, lunch

00:20:01.036 --> 00:20:02.440 align:middle line:90%
like a prince or princess.

00:20:02.440 --> 00:20:03.870 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: We get the point.

00:20:03.870 --> 00:20:06.310 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: So he also
said, eat few suppers

