00:20:10.940 --> 00:20:12.320 align:middle line:90%
as do oils.

00:20:12.320 --> 00:20:14.800 align:middle line:84%
So they should be
consumed early in the day.

00:20:14.800 --> 00:20:18.580 align:middle line:84%
And so the evening
meal should be lighter.

00:20:18.580 --> 00:20:21.857 align:middle line:84%
And so simple adjustments of
when you eat, what you eat

00:20:21.857 --> 00:20:22.940 align:middle line:90%
can make a big difference.

00:20:22.940 --> 00:20:24.773 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: And that'll
make a big differences

00:20:24.773 --> 00:20:27.730 align:middle line:84%
as you wake up in the morning
